Expert advice for Lawns in the month of March 14-03-2019 Expert advice for Lawns in the month of March The information for Lawns in the month of March is given below
The new lawn can be developed during this month, provided assure irrigation system is available. The grass roots/suckers of some selected varieties e.g. Calcutta grass, Korean or selection No.1, can be dibbled in the well prepared soil. Irrigation with the help of sprinkler can be helpful for better establishment of lawn.
